ated epoch, and then\nback to $w_{de}<-1$ eventually. The best-fit result of the case $(n=0, m=-1)$\nwhich is so-called $\\eta$HDE model proposed in \\cite{Huang:2012xm} is the most\nfavorable model and compatible with the $\\Lambda$CDM model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2012 03:41:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Jul 2012 04:00:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
